    title: "Intercreditor Agreements Explained: When Senior and Mezzanine Lenders Clash",
    metaTitle: "Intercreditor Agreements Explained | UK Guide",
    metaDescription: "Understand intercreditor agreements in development finance. Learn how senior and mezzanine lender priorities work, and what happens when a project defaults.",
    excerpt: "A clear explanation of intercreditor agreements in UK development finance, covering how they structure the relationship between senior and mezzanine lenders, and what happens when priorities clash during a default.",
    category: "defaults",
